            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Monster Core pg. 129",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Monster Core",
          "page": 129,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Flame drakes dwell near volcanoes and magma, but it's not unheard of for one to drift into nearby areas like forests or wooded hills. Their scales are usually some shade of red, occasionally fading to smoky blacks and grays along the edges of their wings and the tips of their tails.  \n  \n Rampages of flame drakes often grudgingly live alongside clans of fire giants, rather than be forced from their volcanic homes.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
  "sources": [
